ties-arrangements/Purchasing-property-together/all.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffamilyclic.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FProperties-arrangements%2FPurchasing-property-together%2Fall.shtml&d=dUMwp7fVYmGTcg8TrWfIaIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1ca0af69\" target=\"_blank\">http://familyclic.hk/tc/topics/Properties-arrangements/Purchasing-property-together/all.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"4f80f02116c258a4c1c56ebda46cbc053647d405","tid":641822,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"一般比死者老婆仔女.你要爭就打官司.爭唔爭到都要比一筆律師費.<br />\n居屋應該較複雜.部份係錢部份係褔利.就算出錢一方.都唔一定有全部權益."},{"pid":"cfaa8990d560f441f3a8189f006b1b87d8ac456b","tid":641822,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"咁搞笑"},{"pid":"51f62bcb86f583a341427ba51739c76359f0f3c7","tid":641822,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f80f02116c258a4c1c56ebda46cbc053647d405","tid":641822,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"一般比死者老婆仔女.你要爭就打官司.爭唔爭到都要比一筆律師費.<br />\n居屋應該較複雜.部份係錢部份係褔利.就算出錢一方.都唔一定有全部權益."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"同埋如果仔女要爭既，供樓係你同老婆比既家用，仔女負責毎老豆其他既洗費，最終都未必判曬比樓主/佢朋友。"},{"pid":"7df6f6eb19394d6b943b32f0d989bb1e2b53395e","tid":641822,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"簡單d 份契有冇係手<br />\n睇到如果係單名既打官司啦"},{"pid":"54484acbe9bbb7ddf616a1c129db48f137aa267b","tid":641822,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"未死就上律師樓寫定平安紙<br />\n樓仲洗唔洗供?<br />\n如果差唔多供完贖樓先<br />\n樓契自己keep"},{"pid":"92207c545cb43620871d3cd4e7927125025d2961","tid":641822,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔係律師 <br />\n相關資料亦都睇到我頭暈<br />\n不過你可以睇下咩叫歸復信託(presumed resulting trust)同埋饋贈推定(presumption of advancement)"},{"pid":"22dd4094d6e753b8521df3d1